These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, lawyer, project-manager, musician
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the musician is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the right of the musician##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the project-manager is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the musician is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Job   | musician | entrepreneur     | project-manager | lawyer |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, police-officer, lawyer, electrician
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the police-officer##1
2. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the electrician##1
4. the electrician is on the right of the police-officer##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the nurse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Job     | nurse    | lawyer | police-officer | electrician |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
4 different games are played: whist, poker, billiard, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| Game           | poker | snooker | billiard | whist  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, snowboarding, skateboarding, biathlon
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the egyptian##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Sport         | snowboarding | water-polo | biathlon | skateboarding  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, jet-ski, skateboard
1. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Transport      | bike | roller | jet-ski       | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, juice, soy-milk
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, turquise, green, aquamarine
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who likes green is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person who likes chestnut is between the person who likes green and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | coffee | juice | soy-milk | fanta |
| Color   | turquise | chestnut  | green    | aquamarine  |

