.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking, fishing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, soccer, skiing
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | fishing | filmmaking | board-games | drawing   |
| Sport   | golf | soccer | cycling      | skiing |

