.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, horse, snake
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, baccarat, vegafina, bongani
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the bongani-smoker is on the far right##1
3. the bongani-smoker is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the fish is between the baccarat-smoker and the siglo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish   | horse      | snake      |
| Cigar   | baccarat     | vegafina | siglo | bongani |

