.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, action, martial-arts, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, taxi, tram
1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre       | epic | martial-arts | zombie    | action      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

