.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, bus, roller, car
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, rat, turtle
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Transport   | tram     | bus  | car | roller |
| Pet     | guinea-pig | turtle | hamster     | rat    |

