2. the librarian is on the right of the manager##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the librarian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
