2. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
3. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Color   | purple | apricot | ebony | amber |
| Sport         | parkour  | rugby   | soccer | golf     |

