3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Game      | go | poker    | chess  | monopoly |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | dubstep | indie | punk  |

