2. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's birthday is in may and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Birthday   | april | july  | october  | may |
| Pet           | cat    | hamster | guinea-pig | dog |

