.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-19::.
House: farmhouse, futuristic, wooden, cape-cod
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, security-guard
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
2. the security-guard is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the doctor is on the left of the futuristic house##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the wooden house##1
5. the entrepreneur is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1        |      2       |   3    |   4    |
| House   | cape-cod        | farmhouse       | wooden   | futuristic |
| Job    | security-guard | entrepreneur | doctor | coach  |

